### Mistake #11: `\Throwable` in PHP

**Frequency:** Medium  
**Rule:** AH-E4

```php
// ❌ AI GENERATES THIS
try {
    $result = $this->process();
} catch (\Throwable $e) {
    Logger::error($e->getMessage());
}

// ✅ CORRECT
use Throwable;

try {
    $result = $this->process();
} catch (Throwable $e) {
    Logger::error($e->getMessage());
}
```

