### Mistake #15: Functions with 4+ Parameters

**Frequency:** Low  
**Rule:** AH-S3

```typescript
// ❌ AI GENERATES THIS
function createUser(name: string, email: string, role: string, department: string): User { ... }

// ✅ CORRECT
interface CreateUserParams {
    name: string;
    email: string;
    role: string;
    department: string;
}

function createUser(params: CreateUserParams): User { ... }
```

